  "description": "<p><strong>在接近2年时间的开发以后，Mozilla今天终于在零售商店官方发布了Firefox OS设备。</strong>与此同时，Mozilla也为开发者开启了支付通道，开发者可选择应用收费或应用内的收费。上周，首款商业Firefox OS设备抵达西班牙，由Telefónica开售，Mozilla宣称波兰、哥伦比亚、委内瑞拉也将陆续有产品上市，随后更多国家都会有Firefox OS设备抵达。而今天则是Mozilla官方在零售店内发售Firefox OS设备。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e6b3c14/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244067.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%B6Firefox+OS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244067.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%B6Firefox+OS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244067.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%B6Firefox+OS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244067.htm&amp;t=Mozilla%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%B6Firefox+OS%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3